<P>Improvement (GAO/NSIAD-89-116, Apr.  13, 1989). <BR>

<P>
<P>
<P>Transition Series:  Department of State Issues (GAO/OCG-89-19TR, Nov. <BR>

<P>1988). <BR>

<P>
<P>
<P>State Department's Management of Real Property (GAO/T-NSIAD-89-1,<BR>

<P>Oct.  5, 1988). <BR>

<P>
<P>
<P>Overseas Support:  Current U.S.  Administrative Support System Is Too<BR>

<P>Complicated (GAO/NSIAD-88-84, Mar.  25, 1988). <BR>

